contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionarypar|qu}} '''QU''', '''Qu''' or '''qu''' may refer to: * [[Qu (programming language)]], a computer programming language * [[QU (album)]], an album by the American band Sherwood * [[Qu (poetry)]], a Chinese type of sung poetry * [[qu (digraph)]], a digraph used in several languages. * [[Final Fantasy IX#Setting|Qu]], a race of gourmands from the Square Enix console role-playing game ''Final Fantasy IX'' * [[Qu County]], county in Sichuan, China * qu, [[ISO 639-1]] code for [[Quechua languages|Quechua]], a Native American language of South America * [[East African Airlines]] IATA airline designator * another name for the plant ''[[Myrocarpus frondosus]]'' * a member of the [[History Monks]] in Terry Pratchett's Discworld novels * [[District (PRC and ROC)|Districts]] in the People's Republic of China and the Republic of China ==Academies== * [[Qarshi University]], Lahore, Pakistan * [[Qassim University]], Qassim, Saudi Arabia * [[Qatar University]], Doha, Qatar * [[Queensland University]], Brisbane, Queensland, Australia * [[Queen's University]], Kingston, Ontario, Canada * [[Quincy University]], Quincy, Illinois, United States * [[Quinnipiac University]], Hamden, Connecticut, United States {{disambiguation}}
